2004-06-02  Tor Lillqvist  <tml@iki.fi>

	* configure.ac: Don't use -mwindows on Windows. We don't want
	im-module-file to be a GUI application. And for modules -mwindows
	doesn't matter anyway. Set OS_WIN32 automake variable.

	* src/Makefile.am: Use -no-undefined on Windows, and link
	explicitly with -lintl.

